'''Den-mother''' was a term used for the guardian of [[Squidge]] children. They also had a level of psychic ability, in which [[Otalp]] and [[Remoh (Squidge)|Remoh's]] Den-mother displayed when she said that they would find a storyteller. This turned out to be none other than [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]], who was shot by the [[Vindar]] moments later.

